latestPosts.caption:
SALLY LIGHTFOOT
(Percnon gibbesi)
The Sally Lightfoot is also known as the Nimble spray crab or the Urchin crab. The adults have a carapace which is 30m wide. They have five pairs of walking legs with yellow rings.

SKUNK CLOWNFISH (Amphirion Akallopisos)
The skunk clownfish also known as the nosestripe anemonefish has a light orange colour and has a narrow white stripe running from the mouth to the tail.
